The paper discusses a machine learning technique for semi-supervised classification, which falls under the category of "Machine Learning" (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of Rough Set Theory, which is a subfield of "Artificial Intelligence" (cs.AI) and the use of confidence measures, which is a common technique in "Data Mining" (cs.DM).
